name: Yeti Rambler Colster Slim Can Insulator
description: A beverage sleeve that uses space age tech to controls temps.Double-wall vacuum insulation and a locking gasket retain cold without freezer-burning your hands.18/8 stainless steel survives the long haul and is rustproof.Screw-on ThermoLock™ gasket keeps beverages secure while locking in ice-cold freshness.Fits 355ml slim cans.No Sweat™ technology keeps your hands warm and never feels clammy.
